threads.title: 820-00165 no power on P5v_s4rs3_vfb1
threads.message:
So you get 3V3_S5 at L7560.
What about 3V3_SUS and PM_BATLOW_L?
Be sure to use original Magsafe 2 charger.

threads.title: 820-00165 no power on P5v_s4rs3_vfb1
threads.message:
Post PM_RSMRST_L, PM_PWRBTN_L, PCH_DSWVRMEN, PM_DSW_PWRGD and all RTC signals (4).
Trigger SMC_ONOFF_L and check for drop pulse at PM_PWRBTN_L at same time.
